body_html: Sorry for the additional noise (and additional commit). Having to compile TF with GCC 8.1/OpenMPI 3.1, and thus having to patch some MPI-related code to make it compile, I ported the changes for the PR by hand. Indeed, a closing brace was deleted together with the argument. This (probably) explains the CI tests failures. I'm very sorry for that. Now it should be fixed.

body: Sorry for the additional noise (and additional commit). Having to compile TF with GCC 8.1/OpenMPI 3.1, and thus having to patch some MPI-related code to make it compile, I ported the changes for the PR by hand. Indeed, a closing brace was deleted together with the argument. This (probably) explains the CI tests failures. I'm very sorry for that. Now it should be fixed.
